query:
WITH Ranked AS (
                SELECT 
                    message_root_hash, 
                    chain_id, 
                    block_number,
                    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY chain_id ORDER BY block_number DESC) AS rn
                FROM message_roots
            )
            SELECT message_root_hash, chain_id, block_number
            FROM Ranked
            WHERE rn <= 5
            ORDER BY chain_id, block_number DESC;
